<subSubSection id="3CFB1CCFA344FF89FF52F983BE97F82C" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" type="description">
<paragraph id="745E4F44A344FF89FF52F983BE94F850" blockId="1.[151,1437,1545,2039]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">
A very large series of this species was located in the collection, including 
<specimenCount id="62E784CDA344FF89FC77F983B867F954" box="[994,1139,1655,1679]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" type="generic">21 specimens</specimenCount>
labelled as 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FB66F983B940F954" box="[1267,1364,1655,1679]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">syntypes</typeStatus>
. There are many synonymies within 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FE41F968BE53F968" baseAuthorityName="Gorham" baseAuthorityYear="1880" box="[468,583,1691,1715]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Bicellonycha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amoena">
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FE41F968BDF0F968" box="[468,484,1692,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FE66F968BE53F968" box="[499,583,1692,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">amoena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
including 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FD2EF968BF3CF968" authorityName="Gorham" authorityYear="1881" box="[699,808,1691,1715]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photuris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="facialis">
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FD2EF968BEDFF968" box="[699,715,1692,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FD4CF96FBF3CF968" box="[729,808,1691,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">facialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FCC8F968BFAEF968" box="[861,954,1691,1715]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Bicellonycha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nitida">
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FCC8F968BF79F968" box="[861,877,1692,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">B</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FCE9F96FBFAEF968" box="[892,954,1691,1715]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">nitida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. There was also much more variation within the 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FF2AF94BBD06F90C" box="[191,274,1727,1751]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">syntype</typeStatus>
series than is indicated in 
<bibRefCitation id="107032B5A344FF89FDA5F94BBEC2F90C" author="Gorham, H. S." box="[560,726,1727,1751]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" pagination="29 - 65" refId="ref6258" refString="Gorham, H. S. (1881) Insecta. Coleoptera. Malacodermata. Lampyridae. Biologia Centrali-Americana, 3 (2), 29 - 65." type="journal article" year="1881">Gorham (1881)</bibRefCitation>
including at least three morphotypes. There was however a single male, 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FF4CF917BD38F920" box="[217,300,1763,1787]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">syntype</typeStatus>
specimen bearing a red “type” label. 
<bibRefCitation id="107032B5A344FF89FD54F917BF72F920" author="Gorham, H. S." box="[705,870,1763,1787]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" pagination="29 - 65" refId="ref6258" refString="Gorham, H. S. (1881) Insecta. Coleoptera. Malacodermata. Lampyridae. Biologia Centrali-Americana, 3 (2), 29 - 65." type="journal article" year="1881">Gorham (1881)</bibRefCitation>
also described a female, however this specimen was not found. Due to the confusion regarding what 
<bibRefCitation id="107032B5A344FF89FD03F8F3BF2FF8C4" author="Gorham, H. S." box="[662,827,1799,1823]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" pagination="29 - 65" refId="ref6258" refString="Gorham, H. S. (1881) Insecta. Coleoptera. Malacodermata. Lampyridae. Biologia Centrali-Americana, 3 (2), 29 - 65." type="journal article" year="1881">Gorham (1881)</bibRefCitation>
actually saw versus what was found in the collection, we choose to only designate a 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FE23F8DFBE0FF898" box="[438,539,1835,1859]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Future, more directed research is needed to determine which specimens if any actually constitute the rest of the 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FE41F8BBBE33F8BC" box="[468,551,1871,1895]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">syntype</typeStatus>
series. The male specimen is therefore designated as the 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FB00F8BBB8EEF8BC" box="[1173,1274,1871,1895]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Labels for the designated 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FE85F887BD66F850" box="[272,370,1907,1931]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">lectotype</typeStatus>
specimen are as follows:
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="745E4F44A344FF89FF52F863BE97F82C" blockId="1.[151,1437,1545,2039]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">
“ 
<materialsCitation id="C4894519A344FF89FF44F863BE6BF82C" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="2995532306" collectionCode="TYPE" collectorName="B. C. A. Col." pageId="1" pageNumber="385" specimenCount="3" specimenCount-male="3" typeStatus="lectotype">
Type 
<specimenCount id="62E784CDA344FF89FE9AF863BD30F874" box="[271,292,1943,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
” “Sinanja,/Vera Paz./Champion” “Type.” “ 
<collectorName id="D9142A92A344FF89FD66F863BF77F874" box="[755,867,1943,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">B.C.A.Col.</collectorName>
III.(2)./ 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FC3EF863B819F874" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1833" box="[939,1037,1943,1967]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photuris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Photuris</taxonomicName>
/facialis, 
<specimenCount id="62E784CDA344FF89FBE3F863B89CF874" box="[1142,1160,1943,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
/Gorham” “SYN-/ 
<collectionCode id="12F0D781A344FF89FAD8F863B987F874" box="[1357,1427,1943,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">TYPE</collectionCode>
” “61” “ 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FF4EF84FBD20F808" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1833" box="[219,308,1979,2003]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photuris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Photuris</taxonomicName>
/facialis/Gorham 
<specimenCount id="62E784CDA344FF89FE64F84FBE13F808" box="[497,519,1979,2003]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
”. A red label is added with the following text: “ 
<typeStatus id="AB5AF1E6A344FF89FB9BF84FB8BCF808" box="[1038,1192,1979,2003]" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">LECTOTYPE</typeStatus>
/ 
<taxonomicName id="B3E134C7A344FF89FB25F84FBCD1F82C" authority="Gorham" authorityName="Gorham" authorityYear="1881" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Photuris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="385" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="facialis">
<emphasis id="46959356A344FF89FB25F84FB977F808" box="[1200,1379,1979,2003]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="385">Photuris facialis</emphasis>
Gorham
</taxonomicName>
/Designated by/Martin and Powell 2020”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
